normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n老老豆豆，有冇人試過唔內射都中獎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669bc72255f328faea37961f2bec00b39ed0fa86","tid":358381,"uid":60710,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:33:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友扑野你都咁上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爸爸</blockquote><br />\n因為真係好好好朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae91b35134826da1e2a8b9f44cb96086765a7e10","tid":358381,"uid":119979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T17:38:34.000Z","msg":"你就你啦<br />\n朋友 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09af8dd2d7c8c742e375fe27141642e7d412e0f","tid":358381,"uid":87307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:06:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要過咗幾耐先至可以驗到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真心，食事後藥好傷身。<br />\n女孩子，錫下身啦，食一次事後就等於落一次仔咁傷身啊。<br />\n想扑就做安全措施啦，帶套or食避孕藥or打枝針有幾難。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你要驗，係你發現預計有m嘅時候，但等咗一兩日都仲未有m嘅時候驗就最準。<br />\n你宜家驗粒受精卵都未著床，未改變你身體孕激素，所以未必準架。<br />\n驚就去家計會啦，入面姑娘醫生姑娘都幾好，會幫你搵適合你嘅藥。"},{"pid":"6287ba254e3d04d60bd57d4b4155700a5c945ef4","tid":358381,"uid":89036,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:16:18.000Z","msg":"咁驚青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n9成衰十一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"524e53b6af61dffe9cef74747907b4c4daabfd09","tid":358381,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T18:18:58.000Z","msg":"除非佢無戴套囉如果咪都應該唔洗太驚既<br />\n不過無理由黎m個陣扑